severe malnutrition among
children and local officials
told of

04:01.675 --> 04:06.146 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
32 people starving to
death in the past month.

04:06.146 --> 04:09.983 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
