She's getting the telltale signs
of malnutrition. Her mother

04:58.198 --> 05:01.468 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
pulls back her towel and jacket.

05:01.468 --> 05:08.141 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
