dropping oil prices ripple
through the global economy;

08:40.887 --> 08:46.960 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Mark Shields and David Brooks
analyze the last GOP debate
before Iowa; boosting diversity

08:46.960 --> 09:00.106 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
