oil, but it's more broadly
what's happening in the
commodity

11:06.065 --> 11:11.004 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
complex, and not just the huge
plunge, in and of itself, but
what that says about global

11:11.004 --> 11:14.841 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
