that preceded it.

12:34.887 --> 12:39.826 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think that explains why we
see this sense of urgency and
sometimes panic kick

12:39.826 --> 12:42.862 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
