18:38.851 --> 18:41.287 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. TED CRUZ (R-TX),
Presidential Candidate: My
friend Donald said that he had
had his

18:41.287 --> 18:45.591 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
