field in Iowa.

19:01.173 --> 19:06.612 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. TED CRUZ: I recognize that
Donald is dismayed that his poll
numbers are falling

19:06.612 --> 19:12.351 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
