born abroad is a natural-born
citizen.

19:18.257 --> 19:20.292 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Trump, in
turn, insisted the issue would
hang over his rival's head

19:20.292 --> 19:22.828 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
