19:22.828 --> 19:25.631 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate: And if you become the
nominee, who the hell

19:25.631 --> 19:30.069 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
