19:32.505 --> 19:35.741 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: That set the
tone for a rough-and-tumble
evening, and the candidates

19:35.741 --> 19:39.145 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
got into it again over the Texas
senator's statements that Trump
embodies -- quote -- "New

19:39.145 --> 19:41.747 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
York values."

19:41.747 --> 19:46.318 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. TED CRUZ: And listen, there
