pro-gay-marriage, focus around
money and the media.

19:59.532 --> 20:02.401 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Trump answered
that with a spirited defense of
his hometown, harking

20:02.401 --> 20:05.738 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
