20:05.738 --> 20:11.444 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: And we rebuilt
downtown Manhattan, and
everybody in the world watched
and everybody

20:11.444 --> 20:14.880 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in the world loved New York and
loved New Yorkers. And I have to
tell you, that was

20:14.880 --> 20:17.550 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
