statement that Ted made.

20:17.550 --> 20:19.785 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

20:19.785 --> 20:23.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But it wasn't
