2013 immigration reform
compromise.

20:28.794 --> 20:35.101 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEN. TED CRUZ: It is also the
case that that Rubio-Schumer
amnesty bill, one of the things

20:35.101 --> 20:41.373 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
