Obama's power to let in Syrian
refugees. It enabled hi,

20:41.373 --> 20:45.778 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the president, to certify them
en masse without mandating
meaningful background checks.

20:45.778 --> 20:48.247 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Rubio
counterattacked with a charge
that Cruz himself has gone back
and

20:48.247 --> 20:50.883 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
