20:50.883 --> 20:54.386 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. MARCO RUBIO (R-FL),
Presidential Candidate: Ted
Cruz, you used to say you
supported doubling

20:54.386 --> 20:59.191 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
