21:47.106 --> 21:49.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But Rubio and
Christie saved their toughest
words for the president,
hammering

21:49.475 --> 21:51.944 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
