you. We're against your
policies.

21:55.614 --> 21:58.584 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we are going to kick your
rear end out of the White House
come this fall.

21:58.584 --> 22:00.252 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

22:00.252 --> 22:03.689 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Ohio Governor
John Kasich and former Florida
Governor Jeb Bush also

22:03.689 --> 22:08.194 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
