22:36.255 --> 22:36.755 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome, gentlemen.

22:36.755 --> 22:38.557 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: Thank you, Judy.

