skews to more white women.

40:06.871 --> 40:11.643 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But Baker says
she is encouraged by the
direction Slack is heading.
Seven percent

40:11.643 --> 40:15.079 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of the company's engineers are
African-American. Compare that
with the industry average of

40:15.079 --> 40:20.685 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
1 percent to 2 percent.

40:20.685 --> 40:26.124 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
To change the demographics of an
industry takes time, and one
long-term effort involves

40:26.124 --> 40:30.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
