40:37.101 --> 40:41.105 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JACK DORSEY, CEO, Square: One of
the things I have always loved
about programming and

40:41.105 --> 40:45.209 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
computer science is that you can
truly build something from
scratch.

40:45.209 --> 40:50.315 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: While CEO Jack
Dorsey has not yet publicized
square's diversity figures,

40:50.315 --> 40:54.285 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
his executive team includes
several women in key roles, like
chief financial officer

40:54.285 --> 40:56.554 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and head of engineering.

40:56.554 --> 40:59.457 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VANESSA SLAVICH, Diversity Lead,
Square: At Square, we started at
the top. So, our board

40:59.457 --> 41:03.761 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
