They're driving the company. You
move down to our executive

41:03.761 --> 41:07.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
team, four out nine of the
people who report to Jack are
CEO-quality women who are
running

41:07.865 --> 41:10.835 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a majority of the company.

41:10.835 --> 41:12.904 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so, if we can prioritize
from the top, from our board to
the executive team, inevitably,

41:12.904 --> 41:16.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
it will trickle down.

41:16.040 --> 41:20.478 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Vanessa
Slavich, diversity lead at
Square, says the company is
constantly

41:20.478 --> 41:24.449 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
