will help widen the pool of
prospective employees.

41:24.449 --> 41:29.253 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VANESSA SLAVICH: So, here, we
have a job description for our
data scientist team.

41:29.253 --> 41:33.358 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: One such tool
is Textio. The software uses a
form of artificial intelligence

41:33.358 --> 41:35.993 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to detect bias in the
job descriptions.

41:35.993 --> 41:38.663 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
VANESSA SLAVICH: This
is the before copy.

41:38.663 --> 41:45.403 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: On a scale of
one to 100, it scores 47.
Phrases like rapidly growing

41:45.403 --> 41:52.944 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are regarded as inclusive,
builds relationships feminine,
and words like relentlessly
masculine.

41:52.944 --> 41:57.081 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Once all the changes are made,
the newly revised job
description scores a 95.

41:57.081 --> 42:01.552 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VANESSA SLAVICH: We did a small
anonymous test with our job
descriptions before and

42:01.552 --> 42:04.956 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
after, and they doubled in
applications for both men and
women.

42:04.956 --> 42:09.293 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: While such
efforts can widen the pool of
candidates, Slack's Erica Baker

42:09.293 --> 42:14.332 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
says real, lasting change will
require a cultural shift in the
workplace, taking people beyond

42:14.332 --> 42:16.634 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
their comfort zones.

42:16.634 --> 42:21.539 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ERICA BAKER: People should know
that you're going to feel weird
about talking about race.

42:21.539 --> 42:27.445 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Just like sit with it and, like,
then move past it. But it's
going to get uncomfortable.

42:27.445 --> 42:31.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think people shy away from
talking about those sorts of
things because it is
uncomfortable.

42:31.749 --> 42:37.855 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I think that we need to get
to the uncomfortable spaces to
make good progress.

42:37.855 --> 42:44.095 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Progress will
likely take time, especially
with older and larger companies.

42:44.095 --> 42:46.697 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In our next story, we visit
