the Northerner Mary Phinney.

45:48.879 --> 45:52.149 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARY ELIZABETH WINSTEAD,
Actress: Both feel very
passionately about what they
believe

45:52.149 --> 45:58.289 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in, but, as the series goes on,
you kind of see the complexities
in who they both are,

45:58.289 --> 46:03.761 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and they find ways to connect,
even though they have such
differing views on such very

46:03.761 --> 46:10.801 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
big, big issues. They see the
humanity in one another and are
able to kind of to work

46:10.801 --> 46:14.372 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
alongside each other.

46:14.372 --> 46:21.145 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Ridley Scott
served as executive producer of
the series. It was created and

46:21.145 --> 46:26.817 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
