46:46.370 --> 46:49.507 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID ZABEL, Producer, "Mercy
Street": We wanted to find a way
to find the drama in

46:49.507 --> 46:54.345 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
