story of medical advances during
the Civil War, but infuse

46:54.345 --> 46:58.849 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
it with drama? And Alexandria,
Virginia, became this great
window into all -- a whole bunch

46:58.849 --> 47:03.020 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of different aspects of the war
and all kinds of different
characters.

47:03.020 --> 47:07.692 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It really became much more of a
family saga combined with a
medical drama combined with

47:07.692 --> 47:11.595 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
sort of a wartime epic.

47:11.595 --> 47:17.735 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: One of the most
complex and moving stories in
"Mercy Street" is that of

47:17.735 --> 47:23.674 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
