lot of blood on his sleeve.

47:46.731 --> 47:48.032 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
MCKINLEY BELCHER
III, Actor: Yes.

47:48.032 --> 47:50.201 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
