47:52.703 --> 47:53.671 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The
blood of your love?

47:53.671 --> 47:55.372 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MCKINLEY BELCHER III: Yes,
the blood of my love.

47:55.372 --> 48:01.312 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We did a scene yesterday, all
yesterday, that we were sort of
operating on her, so, yes.

48:01.312 --> 48:05.249 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Actor McKinley
Belcher III told us this role
had special meaning for

48:05.249 --> 48:07.251 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
