proud of this one.

48:47.625 --> 48:52.329 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The producers
also clearly took some pride in
the series' authenticity.

48:52.329 --> 48:59.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A Civil War hospital was no
setting for the squeamish.
Amputations were performed
numerous

48:59.203 --> 49:03.440 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
