take this out -- they're still
sharp and problematical.

49:26.463 --> 49:32.937 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so, this is a capital
amputation saw. They actually
took the saw, you see, around

49:32.937 --> 49:36.807 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
