how you do it, yes.

49:39.577 --> 49:44.381 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DR. STANLEY BURNS: The whole
amputation, if the surgeons were
slow, it would take five

49:44.381 --> 49:49.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
