surgeon could do it, complete an
amputation in two minutes.

49:49.486 --> 49:53.190 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Series creators
Wolfinger and Zabel say they
worked hard for realism and

49:53.190 --> 49:56.160 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
